### 语音识别API测试

### 1. 同步语音识别 - 上传音频文件
POST http://localhost:18080/api/speech/recognize
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="audio"; filename="test.wav"
Content-Type: audio/wav

< /path/to/your/audio/file.wav
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="model"

fun-asr-realtime
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="format"

wav
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="sampleRate"

16000
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="semanticPunctuationEnabled"

false
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="punctuationPredictionEnabled"

true
--boundary--

###

### 2. 异步语音识别 - 上传音频文件
POST http://localhost:18080/api/speech/recognize/async
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="audio"; filename="test.wav"
Content-Type: audio/wav

< /path/to/your/audio/file.wav
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="model"

fun-asr-realtime
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="format"

wav
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="sampleRate"

16000
--boundary--

###

### 3. 创建流式语音识别会话
POST http://localhost:18080/api/speech/streaming/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "fun-asr-realtime",
  "format": "pcm",
  "sampleRate": 16000,
  "semanticPunctuationEnabled": false,
  "punctuationPredictionEnabled": true,
  "maxSentenceSilence": 1300,
  "heartbeat": false,
  "languageHints": ["zh", "en"]
}

###

### 4. 发送音频数据到流式识别会话
POST http://localhost:18080/api/speech/streaming/{{sessionId}}/audio
Content-Type: application/octet-stream

< /path/to/audio/chunk.raw

###

### 5. 停止流式识别
POST http://localhost:18080/api/speech/streaming/{{sessionId}}/stop

###

### 6. 关闭流式识别会话
DELETE http://localhost:18080/api/speech/streaming/{{sessionId}}

###

### 7. 获取流式识别状态
GET http://localhost:18080/api/speech/streaming/status

